   Univ Fed Vicosa, Dept Biol Geral, BR-36570000 Vicosa, MG, Brazil.
   Univ Fed Vicosa, Dept Biol Anim, Programa Posgrad Mestrado Entomol, BR-36570000 Vicosa, MG, Brazil.},
